{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_03_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 私から目を離さないで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "明日は約束の週末だが、調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How's your condition for the promised weekend tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがスケジュールを調整して\n怜ちゃんと一緒に練習出来るようにしてくれたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You adjusted the schedule for me\nso that I can practice with Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6656489587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろとコツを教わることが出来て\nなんとか形にはなってきたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been able to learn various tips‚\nand it's starting to take shape somehow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あとは一ヶ所だけよくミスするところがあるので\nそこさえどうにか出来れば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's just one place where I make a lot of mistakes‚\nso if I can somehow fix that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "明日までにどうにかなりそうなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will you manage it by tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……分かりません……\n怜ちゃんに直接見てもらえれば一番いいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… don't know…\nIt would be best if Rei-chan could see it directly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "今日は怜ちゃんがロケで夜までお仕事だから\n私一人で解決しないといけないんですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rei-chan has a location shoot today until late at night‚\nso I have to solve it on my own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "あとちょっとで出来そうなのに……\nこれで明日までに間に合わなかったらと思うと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm almost there…\nBut if I don't make it by tomorrow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6679062281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、そんな千紗のために\n今日は役に立ちそうなものを持ってきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry. For someone like you‚ Chisa‚\nI brought something that might be useful today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7946284786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、それは……スマホを固定する三脚ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ is that… a tripod to stabilize a smartphone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、これを使って千紗のダンスを撮影する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. We'll use it to record your dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスを撮影して動画を見直すことは\n今までもやってましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been recording and\nreviewing my dances before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5105772234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今回はそれだけじゃない\nこのタブレットを見てくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this time it's not just that.\nTake a look at this tablet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、画面に怜ちゃんが映ってる？\n今日はテレビ番組のロケのはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Rei-chan is on the screen?\nIsn't she supposed to be doing a TV show shoot today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "怜に事務所のタブレットを渡しておいたんだ\nこれならどこにいても千紗を指導出来るだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gave Rei the agency's tablet.\nWith this‚ she can instruct you no matter where she is‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……ロケの合間に撮影した動画を\n見てもらえば、その場でダンスを修正出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… If she can watch the recorded videos\nand correct my dance on the spot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "でもいいんでしょうか、怜ちゃんはお仕事で忙しいのに\n私のせいで休憩時間が無くなるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But is it really okay? Rei-chan is busy with work‚\nand it might take away her break time because of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "怜に聞いたらぜひ協力したいと言ってくれたよ\nきっと今回の件で怜なりに責任を感じているんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked Rei‚ she said she wants to help for sure.\nShe must feel responsible in her own way this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "責任だなんて……\nいつも私が迷惑を掛けてるのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Responsibility…\nI'm always the one causing trouble tho…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3231378328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ありがとう怜ちゃん……\nギリギリまで怜ちゃんに教えてもらえるなら百人力だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ thank you‚ Rei-chan…\nIf I can learn from Rei-chan until the last minute‚ I can do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9117141571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私、最後まで頑張る\n怜ちゃん、遠慮はいらないから厳しく指導してね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do my best until the end.\nRei-chan‚ don't hold back and give me strict guidance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of live performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8121948242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 136
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 136
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 137.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐサニピの出番ですね……\nあれだけ練習したんだから大丈夫……きっと大丈夫……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost time for Sunny Peace performance…\nI practiced so much‚ so it'll be fine… It'll definitely be fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 148.8214335124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか俺まで緊張してきたな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm starting to get nervous too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8214335124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは困ります！\n不安や緊張は人にうつるんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's not good!\nAnxiety and nervousness are contagious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 157.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにはどっしり\n構えてもらわないと私まで不安になっちゃいます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need you‚ {user}-san‚ to stay composed\nOtherwise‚ I'll start feeling anxious too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 164.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗も成長してしっかりしてきたと思ったが\nそういうところは変わってなくて安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you had grown and become more reliable‚ Chisa‚\nBut you haven't changed in that aspect‚ and it's reassuring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "うう……そういう安心はされたくなかったです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I didn't want to be reassured in that way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は誰よりも努力をしてきたじゃないか\nだから自信を持って行って来るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ you've worked harder than anyone else‚ haven't you?\nSo go with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 181.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……\nあれだけ練習したんだから自信を持っていいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right…\nI practiced so much‚ so I can have confidence‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 188.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\n特訓の成果、見せちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san.\nI'll show you the results of my special training!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.333333399997,
          "startTime": 195.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 195.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん！　声援ありがとうございまーす！\n私達のライブ、楽しんでいただけましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Thank you for your cheers!\nDid you enjoy our live performance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "今日はいつも怜ちゃんが踊ってるソロパートを\n私がかわりに踊りました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ instead of Rei-chan‚ who usually dances the solo part‚\nI danced in her place!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けが難しくて何度も挫けそうになったけど\n努力した時間は絶対に無駄じゃないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography was difficult‚ and I felt like giving up many times‚\nBut I believe the time I put into effort was never in vain…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "私も諦めずに頑張り続ければ輝けるんだって\n証明するつもりでステージに立ちました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I stood on this stage to prove that\nif I keep striving without giving up‚ I can shine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "だから、会場のみんなが\n私のダンスで盛り上がってくれて凄く嬉しかったです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I was so happy to see the audience\nGetting excited with my dance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5733.333333299981,
          "startTime": 232.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5966.666666599991,
          "startTime": 232.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "これからも私は絶対に諦めません！\nどんなに辛くても立ち止まったりしません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ I will never give up!\nNo matter how tough it gets‚ I won't stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "全てを出し切って最後まで踊り続けます！\nだからみんな、私から目を離さないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will give it my all and keep dancing until the end!\nSo‚ everyone‚ don't take your eyes off me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "それではラスト一曲いきます！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let's go with the last song!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
