      "text": "ソロパート、凄く良かったって……！\n嬉しい……思い切って挑戦して良かった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said the solo part was really good!\nI'm so happy… It was worth taking the leap and challenging myself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 273.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "よく踊りきったな、千紗\n心なしか千紗の顔も自信に満ちてるように見えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You danced really well‚ Chisa.\nYour face also seems filled with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 280.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか？　でも私なんてまだまだです……\n私一人じゃこんなに強くなれなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really? But I still have a long way to go…\nI couldn't become this strong on my own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 290.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと{user}さんがいたから\n私は勇気を出して挑戦出来たんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because everyone and you‚ {user}-san‚ were there for me\nI was able to gather courage and take on the challenge",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 297.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "私は臆病で、不器用で……\n自分に自信があるなんてまだ言えないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm still timid and goofy…\nI can't say I have confidence in myself yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 304.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs034.m4a",
      "text": "信じて努力し続ければ\n明日の私は今日よりもっと輝けるって分かったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I realized that if I believe and continue to make efforts\nTomorrow‚ I can shine even brighter than today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 311.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs035.m4a",
      "text": "いつか必ず自分に自信を持って\n輝けるようになってみせます。だから見ていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someday‚ I will definitely have confidence in myself\nAnd show that I can shine. So please watch over me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 319.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_03-chs036.m4a",
      "text": "次はもっともっと、{user}さんが\n私から目を離せないようにしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the next performance‚ {user}-san‚\nI will make sure you can't take your eyes off me!",
        "id": ""
